ActCustoms Tariff
Subject“SeaRose FPSO” Repair or Alteration Remission Order, 2012
Precis"SEAROSE FPSO" REPAIR OR ALTERATION REMISSION ORDER, 2012, in order to remit an estimated $9.5 million in customs duties payable by HUSKY OIL OPERATIONS LTD. on the re-importation of the SeaRose Floating Production, Storage and Offloading (FPSO) vessel following maintenance and repair work scheduled to be performed in Northern Ireland starting in or around June 2012.
